item.description:
Due to the weather we are going to have to cancel this Sunday's meetup.

Don't for get there is another meetup scheduled at Mom's & Paws for Sun Mar 10.

http://www.meetup.com/BostonFrenchBulldogs/events/98202982/

Hi everyone, get ready for a SUNDAY meetup at an in-door park called Moms and Paws in Cambridge!

Moms and Paws has a very large indoor space and our last meetup there in December was great!!

Moms and Paws charges $5 per dog to play, or $7 for two. Also if you have additional $$ to donate to the meetup group it is always appreciated.

Your frenchie's canine brothers, sisters and friends are more than welcome to join us at Moms and Paws! Please abide by the weight/size limits they post.

From Moms and Paws: Vaccinations and veterinary paper work on Rabies and DHLP (distemper hepatitis leptorosis parvovirus) are required. Recommended vaccinations are parvo and bordetella. When you come please bring a current list of your dogs vaccinations and your veterinary info (name and phone number). We want to make sure all our dogs are safe :)

Parking: There are many parking spots located on either side of the building. Moms and Paws is located to the side of Work Out World in Cambridge. To get to the front entrance continue on Smith Place and take a left after the WOW sign andÂ building onto Mooney Street. The green signs will indicate our front entrance.

For more information please visit http://momandpaws.com

Thanks so much, we can't wait to see you! Zeek!
